(2376, 'document', 'text/html', 'Thursday', 'general', 'Reception', 'reception', 'Reception', 1, 0, 0, 2372, 0, '', '<p style="line-height:17.8pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;">The wedding weekend starts!!!<span> </span></span></p>\n<p style="line-height:17.8pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;">Please join us after work on Thursday for a ''quiet night in with a takeaway''!! Enjoy the fabulous drive up and get settled infor the weekend.<span> </span>Dinner will be waiting for you.</span></p>\n<p style="line-height:17.8pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;">For those of you who ''d like to come up earlier in the day, thats absolutely fine.<span> </span>All accommodation will be available from 2pm so just let us know what time you expect to arrive and we will be there to meet you!</span></p>\n<p style="line-height:17.8pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:11pt;">Thursday evening will be a relatively quiet one allowing us all to get settled in &amp;catch up over a few beers. <span></span>There is also a billiard room with full sized table for those of you who fancy a game.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;">We cant wait to see you all</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;">Xx</span></p>\n<p><img src="../../assets/users/paulandmary/images/lochaline-castle-d2958c83.bmp" alt="" /></p>', 1, 33, 3, 1, 0, 1, 1346244856, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Reception', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2377, 'document', 'text/html', 'Friday', 'general', 'Wedding Schedule', 'wedding-schedule', 'Wedding Schedule', 1, 0, 0, 2372, 0, '', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:15.75pt;margin:0cm 0cm 15.75pt;"><strong><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">FRIDAY DAYTIME ACTIVITIES</span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-18pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt;"><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Clay pigeon shooting: </span></span></strong><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Prepare to have ''a blast'' as you turn your hand to the favoured outdoor pursuit of clay pigeon shooting.... who knows, it couldturn out to be the start of a whole new hobby. </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">The session will include all the necessary technique&amp; safety training from a member of the Morvern Gun Club before you step up to test your aim and accuracy! Its a 30 bird shoot (including clays, cartridges, gun hire, tea/coffee on site and lunch). 40pp.<span> </span>Maximum number is 20 </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:15.75pt;margin:0cm 0cm 10pt;"><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:12pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-21.3pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 21.3pt;"><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Golf:</span></span></strong><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"> If a morning on the golf course is your thingthere will be a bus leaving the estate on Friday morning to take you over to the Isle of Mull for a round at Craignure golf club. Cost is 27pp and includes the bus, ferry crossing and green fees. <span></span></span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;"><a href="http://www.craignuregolfclub.co.uk/"><span style="color:#800080;font-size:13.5pt;">http://www.craignuregolfclub.co.uk/</span></a></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:-21.3pt;margin:0cm 0cm 10pt 21.3pt;"><span style="line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="line-height:115%;font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="line-height:115%;font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Fishing<span></span>Loch &amp; River: </span></span></strong><span style="line-height:115%;font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">River fishing </span><span style="line-height:115%;font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:13.5pt;">is available however; there isn''t much around in the river this early in the season. If you do fancy your chances though, we can arrange it. 5pp. <span></span>Maximum of 12 rods.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin:0cm 0cm 10pt 21.3pt;"><span style="line-height:115%;font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:13.5pt;">A better bet would be fishing the lochs. This is free for all of us staying on the Estate. There are also boats available to hire if youd prefer that to fishing from the bank (30 for a boat, 45 for a boatwith engine).<span> </span>There are 3 boats available on Loch Arienas &amp; one on Loch Teanait. There is no limit on the number of rods for the lochs unless of course you would like boats! </span><span style="line-height:115%;font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"><a href="http://www.ardtornish.co.uk/Pages/FISHING.asp"><span style="line-height:115%;color:#800080;">http://www.ardtornish.co.uk/Pages/FISHING.asp</span></a></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-42pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Cycling:</span></span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"> </span></strong><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">There are bikes available for hire from the estate 15</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:Georgia, serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-18pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 18pt;"><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Beautician:</span></span></strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">We are delighted to have Gil one of her girls<span> </span>from Senses Spa pampering us for the day! Ive been to their salon in Comrie many times and can highly recommend them! They will be offering the following treatments:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-18pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:Georgia, serif;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Eve Taylor Facial 20</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Aromatic Back, Neck &amp; Shoulder Massage 20</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Tan 35</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">OPI Manicure20</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">OPI Pedicure 25 (there is a typo on your wedding passport which says 35!)</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Eyebrow Threading 8</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Here is a link to their salon website if youd like any further details on the treatments theyll be offering.<span> </span></span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:10.5pt;"><span></span><a href="http://www.sensesspa.co.uk/"><span style="color:#800080;font-size:13.5pt;">http://www.sensesspa.co.uk/</span></a></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-14.7pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Or a lazy day</span></span></strong><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"> Perhaps you just want to do nothing! </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:8.7pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 36pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:2.7pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Have a long lie, go for a walk around the estate or ventured into the village for lunchdo whatever takes your fancy. </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:36pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Please let us know via your RSVP which activity (s) you fancy and we will get it all organised for you! If youve returned your RSVP and you then decide you fancy booking anything else please just drop is a message and well get it organised. </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">4pm EVERYONE BACK TO ACHRANICH FOR THE HIGHLAND GAMES</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">We really wanted to organise something fun and that didnt just involve an evening of refreshments!</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">After weeks racking our brains as to what would be appropriate something a little out of the ordinary even. we hit upon it!!! Wed have our very own Highland Games!! </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Scotland has played host to Highland games since times immemorial indeed, Lochaline hosts its own every July. So we thought, why not! We will enjoy a unique version of this Scottish classic.with the following events:</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-18pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Toss the caber</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-18pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Wellie Flinging</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-18pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Tug o war</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-18pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Haggis Hurling</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;text-indent:-18pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt 42pt;"><span style="font-family:Symbol;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span><span style="font-family:''Times New Roman'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:7pt;"> </span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Malt Whisky challenge</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">We will have our own Chieftain, Piper and of course prizesfor the winners!</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:Georgia, serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">7pm B.Y.O.B. PARTY</span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">Friday night shenanigans! This will be a casual night in the Marquee. Its back to basics with wellies, jeans and jackets.. Its not a night for dressing up although, if you really want to, then thats absolutely fine too!!</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"><strong>FOOD:</strong> A hog Roast (the veggies won''t be forgotten) will be served about 7pm and it will simply be a case of tucking in. </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"><strong>BOOZE:</strong>There will be beer kegs provided for you to help yourself if thats your drink of choice. Otherwise, bring along whatever tipple takes your fancy as there wont be a bar as such.there will however be glasses, ice and mixers etc </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:15.75pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:Arial, ''sans-serif'';color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"><strong>MUSIC:</strong> We recently went to see Pauls nephew Callum play his first gig at the Barrowlands.<span> </span>We were so impressed that weve roped him in to play for us on the Friday night! </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;font-size:13.5pt;">We know there are a few other musicians amongst you and wed be delighted if you felt the desire to get behind the mike! </span></p>\n<p></p>', 1, 33, 4, 1, 0, 1, 1346244856, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Wedding Schedule', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
