(7, 'document', 'text/html', 'FAQS', 'FAQS', 'FAQS', 'wedding-faqs', 'FAQS', 1, 0, 0, 3, 0, 'Get the answers to some common questions asked by website users...', '<h2 class="dec">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>\r\n<p>Please feel free and contact us at support [at] theweddingwebsitegroup.com with any questions you might have.</p>\r\n<div id="faqs">\r\n<h3>Are there any additional charges other than the initial purchase price?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>No, the price you pay is for the package you choose and lasts for one year only. You will need to contact us if you want to extend beyond the year sign up period. An option to ''extend'' your current package will be available in a future add-on.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Do I get a free .co.uk or .com domain with my website?</h3>\r\n<div class="justifyright">\r\n<p>Your Free domain name will be a prefix of the ''TheWeddingWebsiteGroup.com''.<br />So for instance if you want to have ''alex-and-jo'' the domain name would be ''http://alex-and-jo.theweddingwebsitegroup.com<br />If you do want your own personal domain name , we can buy this for you, please email to <strong><a title="contact the wedding website group" href="mailto:info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com">info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com</a></strong>stating what domain name you would like and we can forward details of costs.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Can I have more space to enable me to have more photographs on my website?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Yes we have 3 packages that should suffice for most people. The top package allows 1000MB of space. This equates to around 300+ photos if each photo is 3MB.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>I am concerned about any personal information on my website appearing on the search engines, can I prevent my site from appearing in a web search?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Yes. You have the option to prevent search engines from indexing your website in your ''website settings'' panel. You can also password protect the entire site.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>How can I make a suggestion for the website?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Please contact <strong><strong><a title="contact the wedding website group" href="mailto:info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com">info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com</a></strong></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>How can I report a problem?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>Please contact <strong><a title="contact the wedding website group" href="mailto:info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com">info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com</a></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>How many photos can I upload to my website?</h3>\r\n<div>\r\n<p>It depends on the physical file size of each photo. If each photo is 3 MB (typical size) then the basic package of 100MB would allow for approximately 33 images. However if your photos are only 1 MB each you could have up to 200 photos with the basic package.<br />You must also ensure that your photos are the correct resolution at 72dpi, if you have any problems please email us at <strong><a title="contact the wedding website group" href="mailto:info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com">info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com</a></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /faq-styles -->\r\n<script type="text/javascript">// <![CDATA[\r\n	$(document).ready(function() {\r\n  $(''#faqs h3'').each(function() {\r\n    var tis = $(this), state = false, answer = tis.next(''div'').hide().css(''height'',''auto'').slideUp();\r\n    tis.click(function() {\r\n      state = !state;\r\n      answer.slideToggle(state);\r\n      tis.toggleClass(''active'',state);\r\n    });\r\n  });\r\n});\r\n// ]]></script>', 1, 42, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1299013700, 1, 1356698217, 0, 0, 0, 1299013680, 1, '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(8, 'document', 'text/html', 'Contact', 'Contact', 'Contact', 'contact', 'Contact', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '<h2 class="dec">We''re here to help</h2>\r\n<p>Couldn''t find an answer in our FAQ section or want to know more about The Weddimg Website Group?<br />Complete the form below and we''ll get back to you as soon as possible.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n[[!FormIt?\r\n&amp;hooks=`email,redirect,recaptcha`\r\n&amp;validate=`\r\ncontact_name:required,\r\ncontact_email:email:required,\r\ncontact_comments:required`\r\n&amp;emailTpl=`emailContactTpl`\r\n&amp;emailSubject=`Message from website`\r\n&amp;emailTo=`janice@9thwave.co.uk`\r\n&amp;redirectTo=`2357`\r\n&amp;submitVar=`pageContactFormToken`\r\n]]\r\n</p>\r\n<form id="contactForm" action="[[~[[*id]]]]" method="post">\r\n	<fieldset>\r\n		<input name="pageContactFormToken" type="hidden" value="1" />\r\n	</fieldset>\r\n	\r\n	<fieldset>\r\n<div>[[!+fi.validation_error_message]]</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>\r\n				<label for="contact_name">Your Name</label>\r\n				<input id="contact_name" class="text" name="contact_name" type="text" value="[[!+fi.contact_name]]" />\r\n				[[!+fi.error.contact_name]]\r\n			</li>\r\n<li>\r\n				<label for="contact_email">Your Email</label>\r\n				<input id="contact_email" class="text" name="contact_email" type="text" value="[[!+fi.contact_email]]" />\r\n				[[!+fi.error.contact_email]]\r\n			</li>\r\n<li>\r\n				<label for="contact_comments">Comments</label>\r\n				<textarea id="contact_comments" name="contact_comments">[[!+fi.contact_comments]]</textarea>\r\n				[[!+fi.error.contact_comments]]\r\n			</li>\r\n<li>[[+formit.recaptcha_html]]\r\n[[!+fi.error.recaptcha]]\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n				<button>Send Message</button>\r\n			</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</fieldset>\r\n</form>\r\n<div class="divider-690"></div>\r\n<p>\r\nWe are a UK based company tucked away in Bradford in the north of England. We currently do not have a contact number for any enquiries but you can be sure to get a quick response from using the above form or contacting us directly <a href="mailto:info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com">here</a></p>', 1, 2, 14, 1, 0, 1, 1299013717, 1, 1346690242, 0, 0, 0, 1299013680, 1, 'Contact', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
