(2343, 'document', 'text/html', 'Home', 'general', 'home', 'home', 'home', 1, 0, 0, 2342, 0, '', '<h1>Welcome to our wedding website</h1>\r\n<p><img class="justifyleft" src="assets/users/someoneandsomebody/images/img-home-111f72aa.jpg" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>Hi everyone.<br /><br />Heres our very own Wedding Website! You will find all the details youneed about our wedding.Come back often as we will keepposting updates, pictures, events,and other content to keep you all in the loop.<br /><br />It is hard to believe we have been in a relationship for almost 9 years. 9 years!! Im sure this 9th year will be one that keeps us on our toes getting ready for our big day.<br /><br />Dont forget to RSVP if you still havent done so. You can also share your thoughts or comments about us in our wedding guestbook. To know more about our love story, please visit engagement story and our story.<br /><br />All this journey has been fun and we thought it would be a good idea to share this with you...<br /><br /></p>', 1, 65, 0, 1, 0, 1, 1346181474, 1, 1355482122, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Home', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1);
