(2344, 'document', 'text/html', 'Our Story', 'general', 'Our Story', 'our-story', 'Our Story', 1, 0, 0, 2342, 0, '', '<h1>Our Story</h1>\n<p>Well where do we start....</p>\n<p>It was 2001 when Bobby and I met in a dodgy nightclub in Nottingham. We had noticed each other on previous nights out but the first time we spoke was in May 2001 whilst at the bar buying our favourite tipple of Brandy and Babycham. There was an instant spark and we spent the rest of the night chatting away and putting the world to rights.</p>\n<p>We met the following few weekends in the same nightclub and finally decided to move out of our comfort zone and embark on our first date. A comparatively formal affair in an Indian restaurant we had a great night and have never looked back.</p>\n<p>Fast forward to 2011 Bobby and I decided to get engaged and here we are looking forward to our Big Day in March 2013. We weren''t going to have a ''big do'' but as is often the case, over excitement has taken hold and we find ourselves organising pre-wedding events and post-wedding events...hey ho:-)</p>\n<p>We hope all our family and friends will enjoy all the events and also this website which we hope you will find useful and informative.</p>\n<p>Thank you for reading....<a href="http://someoneandsomebody.theweddingwebsitegroup.com/sign-guestbook.html">now go leave us a message.</a></p>', 1, 65, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1346181474, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Our Story', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
