(2373, 'document', 'text/html', 'Home', 'general', 'home', 'home', 'home', 1, 0, 0, 2372, 0, '', '<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;">Welcome to our wedding website....</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;">We hopeyou will find all the information you''ll need to join us in celebrating not only our special day but our wedding weekend! </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;">In the website you can RSVP, find out more info about the ceremony, the location and.. most importantly, how to get to Ardtornish!</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;">Were so excited about the wedding &amp; are really looking forward to sharing our day with each and every one of you. We appreciate that it means a day off work and also, a 3 hour drive north for most of you but, we really do hope that you canjoin us. Its a beautiful part of the country, perfect for a few days relaxation, fun and a wedding!</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">We''d love it if you upload / view pictures from the wedding, stag &amp; hen do''s or indeed, share with usany pictures from the past. Please alsoleave us a message viaonline Guest Book.</span></span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;">Paul &amp;Mary x</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><img src="../../assets/users/paulandmary/images/ians-wedding-0cd5d167.jpg" alt="" /></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;"></span></p>\n<p></p>', 1, 33, 0, 1, 0, 1, 1346244856, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Home', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2374, 'document', 'text/html', 'Our Story', 'general', 'Our Story', 'our-story', 'Our Story', 1, 0, 0, 2372, 0, '', '<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">We first met on a blind date courtesy of a couple of friends  you know who you are! The outcome was never certain after Mary was given a description of me as a ''nice wee guy'' (she likes her fella''s to be tall) and as such, had her exit strategy in the form of friends in a pub around the corner already lined up!</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">It was a miserable, wet Wednesday evening in November 2007 whereby we met for a quick drink at the Living Room on St. Vincent Street in Glasgow.<span></span>I am sure this will come as no surprise to any of you...........a quick drink soon turned into far too many glasses of wine and nonstop chatter till closing time!!<span> </span>A week or so later, a we met again at an dinner in Edinburgh and the rest as they say, is history!</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">The past 5 years have flown by in a whirlwind of fun and adventure. The meeting oftwopeoplewith an overwhelming desire to travel hasnt been a formula for staying home!<span> </span>As such, weve been lucky enough to enjoy many amazing trips during the past few years, experiencing many new cultures and lots of amazing new food!!<span> </span></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:Arial;font-size:medium;"><img src="../../assets/users/paulandmary/images/us-on-the-boat2-1f9e3da8.jpg" alt="" /></span></p>', 1, 33, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1346244856, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Our Story', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2375, 'document', 'text/html', 'Wedding Party', 'general', 'Ceremony', 'ceremony', 'Ceremony', 1, 0, 0, 2372, 0, '', '<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;">We are keeping it simple!<span> </span>One Bridesmaid and one Bestman!! </span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;">Jacqui Mackintosh  our beautiful bridesmaid and Marys little sister.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><img src="../../assets/users/paulandmary/images/bridesmaid-f2aeadc6.jpg" alt="" /></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;">Andy Stirling  the best man to keep Paul on the straight and narrow, apparently.</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><img src="../../assets/users/paulandmary/images/andy-pic-19f9ba56.jpg" alt="" /></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;font-size:12pt;"></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">Whilst weve kept the official wedding party small.... we''ve enlisted the help of several others who we fondly refer to as the unofficial wedding party. All of whom deserve a big thank you! </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;"></span></span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">Youve all helpedin manyways, assisting us with arrangements and more importantly, youve all been there to keep us sane over the past few months and for that, we cant thank you enough. One memorable such time was the pre-wedding trip to LA to suss out the lay of the land.</span></span></p>\n<p><img src="../../assets/users/paulandmary/images/la-073bbc59.jpg" alt="" /></p>', 1, 33, 2, 1, 0, 1, 1346244856, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ceremony', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2351, 'document', 'text/html', 'Gift List', 'general', 'Gift List', 'gift-list', 'Gift List', 1, 0, 0, 2342, 0, '', '<h1>Gift List</h1>\n<p>What can you give the couple who have everything?<br />The answer is nothing really...but we do have a few charities we''d like to suggest for donations. Please do not feel you have to give anything but below is a list of charities we support.</p>\n<p><a title="webpods" href="http://www.webpods.co.uk">The Big Charity<br /></a>One of the most valuable charities in the world.</p>\n<p>We will be adding more charities soon.</p>\n<h1></h1>', 1, 65, 8, 1, 0, 1, 1346181474, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Gift List', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
