(2348, 'document', 'text/html', 'Wedding Party', 'general', 'Wedding Party', 'wedding-party', 'Wedding Party', 1, 0, 0, 2342, 0, '', '<h1>The Wedding Party</h1>\n<h2></h2>\n<p><img class="justifyleft" src="../../assets/users/someoneandsomebody/images/asleep-e77a6ede.jpg" alt="" width="220" height="143" /></p>\n<h2>Someone</h2>\n<p>The bride will wake up for the wedding we promise you!<br />Here she is though dreaming about the big day and all the shenanigans that go with it.<br />Happy days!</p>\n<p></p>\n<hr /><h2><img class="justifyleft" src="../../assets/users/someoneandsomebody/images/cartwheel-b5ee7a11.jpg" alt="" width="222" height="148" /></h2>\n<h2>Somebody</h2>\n<p>Here is the delighted partner exercising mind and body in anticipation of the big day.</p>\n<p></p>', 1, 65, 5, 1, 0, 1, 1346181474, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Wedding Party', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2349, 'document', 'text/html', 'Accommodation', 'general', 'Accommodation', 'accommodation', 'Accommodation', 1, 0, 0, 2342, 0, '', '<h1>Accommodation</h1>\n<p>There are a number of options for your stay in the area if you do not want to stay at the hotel itself.</p>\n<h2>The Red Lion</h2>\n<p>A lovely traditional pub just 3 miles from the reception venue.<br /><strong>Tel:</strong> 01234 567890<br /><strong>Email:</strong> theowner@theredlioninbuxtonnot.co.uk<br /><strong>Address:</strong> Victoria Lane, Buxton, DE24 7TP</p>\n<h2>Coopers Bed &amp; Breakfast</h2>\n<p>Coopers B&amp;B is about 4 miles from the venue, there are 4 ensuite rooms with 2 more rooms having a shared bathroom.<br /><strong>Tel:</strong> 01234 567890<br /><strong>Email:</strong> theowner@coopersbandbnot.co.uk<br /><strong>Address:</strong> 251 Bloomers Road, Buxton, DE25 3ER</p>\n<p>Let us know if you are struggling to find accommodation and we will do our best to help you out.<br /><br /></p>\n<p></p>\n<h1></h1>', 1, 65, 6, 1, 0, 1, 1346181474, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Accommodation', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2347, 'document', 'text/html', 'Wedding Schedule', 'general', 'Wedding Schedule', 'wedding-schedule', 'Wedding Schedule', 0, 0, 0, 2342, 0, '', '<h1>The Wedding Schedule</h1>\r\n<p>This is a sample page of how you might want to lay out the content:</p>\r\n<h4>2pm - Arrivals at the ceremony</h4>\r\n<p>Ushers 45 minutes before; best man and groom 45-30 minutes\r\nbefore; guests: up to 30 minutes before; groom''s parents: 15\r\nminutes before; mother of bride and bridesmaids ten minutes before;\r\nbride and father five minutes before.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4>The ceremony</h4>\r\n<p>Should last around 30 minutes.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4>Photographs</h4>\r\n<p>20-30 minutes<br /><em>Note: Allow approximately ten minutes for pictures of the\r\nbride and groom, ten to twenty minutes for other shots.</em></p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4>Drinks Reception</h4>\r\n<p>90 minutes, usually extends to two hours</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style="font-size: 1em;">The wedding meal</h4>\r\n<p>2 hours for a three course meal.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4>8pm - Evening reception</h4>\r\n<p>Dancing, singing and general merriment will continue until the last guest drops.</p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>The following is a rough timeline for the big day, from the ceremony to the end of the reception.</p>\r\n<h3>Arrivals at the Ceremony</h3>\r\n<p>Ushers 45 minutes before; best man and groom 45-30 minutes\r\nbefore; guests: up to 30 minutes before; groom''s parents: 15\r\nminutes before; mother of bride and bridesmaids ten minutes before;\r\nbride and father five minutes before.</p>\r\n<h3>Church or Civil Ceremony</h3>\r\n<p>20-60 minutes (civil ceremonies are shorter than religious\r\nones)</p>\r\n<p><em>N.B. Allow plenty of time to get from the ceremony venue to\r\nthe reception, if applicable, especially if the area is prone to\r\nheavy traffic.</em></p>\r\n<h3>Photographs</h3>\r\n<p>20-30 minutes</p>\r\n<p><em>Note: Allow approximately ten minutes for pictures of the\r\nbride and groom, ten to twenty minutes for other shots.</em></p>\r\n<h3>Drinks Reception</h3>\r\n<p>90 minutes, usually extends to two hours</p>\r\n<p><em>Note: A receiving line takes about 40 minutes and well\r\norganised photographs take 20-30 minutes.</em></p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">Seating Guests</span></h3>\r\n<p>Up to 30 minutes.</p>\r\n<h3>The Wedding Meal</h3>\r\n<p>Two hours for three courses.</p>\r\n<h3>Speeches</h3>\r\n<p>30 minutes, usually extending to 45 minutes (at least ten\r\nminutes per person, assuming there are three speakers).</p>\r\n<h3>Cake Cutting</h3>\r\n<p>15-20 minutes.</p>\r\n<p>Approximately three hours.</p>\r\n<p><em>Note: This depends upon when the bride and groom leave, and\r\nhow long the party lasts, and the style of the\r\nvenue/reception.</em></p>\r\n</div>', 1, 65, 4, 1, 0, 1, 1346181474, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Wedding Schedule', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2346, 'document', 'text/html', 'Reception', 'general', 'Reception', 'reception', 'Reception', 1, 0, 0, 2342, 0, '', '<h1>The Reception</h1>\n<p>There will be two parts to the reception, the first will be the meal where we can only have a maximum of 80 guests. The second half will be the big partty:-)</p>\n<p>The reception will be held at:<br /><strong>Crown Hill Hall</strong><br />Derbyshire, DE13 4RT<br /><strong>Tel:</strong> 01234 567890</p>\n<p><strong>4pm - Champagne reception</strong></p>\n<p>We will congregate in the main hall where we will have a short toast and a few photographs.<br />Photographs will also be taken in the grounds, this should take around 40 minutes.</p>\n<hr /><p><strong>5pm - The meal</strong></p>\n<p>We will sit down for our meal at 5pm</p>\n<hr /><p><strong>6:30pm - Speeches</strong></p>\n<p>Time for the speeches which we anticipate will last about 30 minutes.</p>\n<hr /><p><strong>7pm - Champagne reception and evening proceedings</strong></p>\n<p>After the speeches we can all congregate again in the main hall where we will have another champagne toast and then down to the cellar bar for the evening do. The evening will wind down at around 1am, the bar will close at midnight bu which time i think we will be absolutely spent!</p>\n<h1></h1>', 1, 65, 3, 1, 0, 1, 1346181474, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Reception', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2345, 'document', 'text/html', 'Ceremony', 'general', 'Ceremony', 'ceremony', 'Ceremony', 1, 0, 0, 2342, 0, '', '<h1>The Ceremony</h1>\n<p>Here are the ceremony details:</p>\n<p>St Margarets Church<br />Cooper Street<br />Matlock<br />DE13 5TP<br /><br /><strong>Start:</strong> 2pm<br /><strong>Finish:</strong> 2:30pm</p>\n<p>There will be 20 minutes of photographs after the ceremony and then we will get the car to the reception. If you need any help with getting to and from the church or the reception please get in touch.</p>\n<p>You can email us: <a href="mailto:alexandbobby@myemailclient.com">alexandbobby@myemailclient.com</a></p>\n<h1></h1>', 1, 65, 2, 1, 0, 1, 1346181474, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Ceremony', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2086, 'document', 'text/html', 'Home', 'general', 'home', 'home', 'home', 1, 0, 0, 2085, 0, '', '<h1>Welcome to our website!</h1>\r\n<p>\r\n<br />\r\n<img class="justifyleft" src="assets/templates/wedding/wed-themes/images/img-home.jpg" alt="" width="251" height="187" /></p>\r\n<p>Hi everyone.</p>\r\n<p>Here''s our very own Wedding Website! You will find all the details you need about our wedding day. Come back often as we will keep posting updates, pictures, events, and other content to keep you all in the loop.</p>\r\n<p>It is hard to believe we have been in a relationship for almost 7 years. 7 years!! I''m sure this 7th year will be one that keeps us on our toes getting ready for our big day.</p>\r\n<p>Don''t know forget to RSVP if you still haven''t done so. You can also share your thoughts or comments about us in our wedding guestbook.</p>\r\n<p>We have added a gift list for anyone who insists on getting us a present and you can find out where to stay if you are travelling the miles to be with us.</p>\r\n<p>All this journey has been fun and we thought it will be a good idea to share this with you...</p>\r\n<p>We hope you enjoy it as much as we have.</p>', 1, 37, 0, 1, 0, 1, 1340018231, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Home', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
