(2534, 'document', 'text/html', 'Guest Blogging', 'Guest Blogging', 'Guest Blogging', 'guest-blogging', 'Guest Blogging', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, '', '<h2 class="dec">Write For Us  Guest Post Opportunity</h2>\r\n<p>Here at <a href="http://theweddingwebsitegroup.com/">TheWeddingWebsite.com</a> we would like to invite all new writers and regular bloggers/guest posters to <strong>publish a guest post</strong> on our blog. You don''t have to be a professional blogger; anyone with an interest in weddings and civil partnerships can contribute.</p>\r\n<p>We love to build contacts with similar minded poeple and share links. So, if you think you could write about your upcoming/past wedding or if you''re a vendor wanting some FREE advertising, then we would like to hear from you!</p>\r\n<h4>What If I''ve Never Written For A Blog Before?</h4>\r\n<p>Don''t worry, we have a professional copywriter to help out. She will look at the content you send and make any necessary changes. We won''t publish the article without your consent.</p>\r\n<h4>What Should I Write About?</h4>\r\n<p>We are only looking for content that matches our criteria of weddings and civil partnerhips. Here is a\r\n list of some general subjects that you can look into when you want to \r\nwrite for us;</p>\r\n<ul class="list-items">\r\n<li><strong>Engaged or Married Couples</strong> - Write about your experiences along with any photographs.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Wedding Photographers, Wedding Venues, Florists, Wedding Vendors</strong> - Blog about your experiences and post your favourite snaps. </li>\r\n<li><strong>Wedding DIY Projects</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Guest Post Submission Guidelines</h4>\r\n<ul class="list-items">\r\n<li>Posts must be AT LEAST! <strong>200+ words</strong> long or include 4+ quality images...preferably more on both counts but we will assess each post and offer assistance where we think it''s needed.</li>\r\n<li>All images must be 72dpi (we can help covert images in a higher resolution if required).</li>\r\n<li>Images should be a size of at least 600pixels wide.</li>\r\n<li>We only accept articles that are written in English at this moment.</li>\r\n<li>Articles must be written by you and totally original! We will be checking ALL submissions for breach of copyright.</li>\r\n<li>We reserve the right to correct spelling &amp; grammar and add any additional images needed to make the article more visually \r\nappealing.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Giving You Credit and Free Advertising</h4>\r\n<p>We want to share links that will be beneficial to both parties and so if your submission is successful we will publish a short bio about you or your company including backlinks to your website.</p>\r\n<h4>Write For Us &amp; Submit a Guest Post!!!</h4>\r\n<p>Fill out the form below and let us know what you''d like to write about.<br />We look forward to hearing from you and reading your submission.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n[[!FormIt?\r\n&amp;hooks=`email,redirect,recaptcha`\r\n&amp;validate=`\r\ncontact_name:required,\r\ncontact_email:email:required,\r\ncontact_comments:required`\r\n&amp;emailTpl=`emailContactTpl`\r\n&amp;emailSubject=`Message from website`\r\n&amp;emailTo=`info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com`\r\n&amp;redirectTo=`2357`\r\n&amp;submitVar=`pageContactFormToken`\r\n]]\r\n</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<form id="contactForm" action="[[~[[*id]]]]" method="post">\r\n	<fieldset>\r\n		<input name="pageContactFormToken" type="hidden" value="1" />\r\n	</fieldset>\r\n	\r\n	<fieldset>\r\n<div>[[!+fi.validation_error_message]]</div>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li class="no-border">\r\n				<label for="contact_name">Your Name</label>\r\n				<input id="contact_name" class="text" name="contact_name" type="text" value="[[!+fi.contact_name]]" />\r\n				[[!+fi.error.contact_name]]\r\n			</li>\r\n<li class="no-border">\r\n				<label for="contact_email">Your Email</label>\r\n				<input id="contact_email" class="text" name="contact_email" type="text" value="[[!+fi.contact_email]]" />\r\n				[[!+fi.error.contact_email]]\r\n			</li>\r\n<li class="no-border">\r\n				<label for="contact_comments">What do you want to write about?</label>\r\n				<textarea id="contact_comments" style="height: 160px;" name="contact_comments">[[!+fi.contact_comments]]</textarea>\r\n				[[!+fi.error.contact_comments]]\r\n			</li>\r\n<li class="no-border">[[+formit.recaptcha_html]]\r\n[[!+fi.error.recaptcha]]\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n				<button>Send Message</button>\r\n			</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</fieldset>\r\n</form>', 1, 2, 15, 1, 0, 1, 1354710798, 1, 1356698735, 0, 0, 0, 1354710840, 1, 'Guest Blogging', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2504, 'document', 'text/html', 'Home', 'general', 'home', 'home', 'home', 1, 0, 0, 2503, 0, '', '<h1>Welcome to our wedding website</h1>\n<p>It''s been great having a website to let all our family and friends know what the latest developments are. We will be sending out invites to our celebration events very soon.</p>\n<p>Lets add a link to one of the other pages within our website such as the <a title="jo bloggs blog" href="http://jobloggs.theweddingwebsitegroup.com/blog/">Blog page</a>. First we need to visit the blog page and copy the website address (URL).</p>\n<p><img src="../../assets/users/jobloggs/images/on-bench-712e0a5e.jpg" alt="" width="586" height="428" /></p>\n<p></p>', 1, 63, 0, 1, 0, 1, 1352982252, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Home', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
