(1847, 'document', 'text/html', 'Home', 'general', 'home', 'home', 'home', 1, 0, 0, 1846, 0, '', '<h3>Welcome to our wedding website!</h3>\n<p>\n<br />\n<img class="justifyleft" src="assets/templates/wedding/wed-themes/images/img-home.jpg" alt="" width="251" height="187" /></p>\n<p>Hi everyone.</p>\n<p>Here''s our very own Wedding Website! You will find all the details you need about our wedding day. Come back often as we will keep posting updates, pictures, events, and other content to keep you all in the loop.</p>\n<p>It is hard to believe we have been in a relationship for almost 7 years. 7 years!! I''m sure this 7th year will be one that keeps us on our toes getting ready for our big day.</p>\n<p>Don''t know forget to RSVP if you still haven''t done so. You can also share your thoughts or comments about us in our wedding guestbook.</p>\n<p>We have added a gift list for anyone who insists on getting us a present and you can find out where to stay if you are travelling the miles to be with us.</p>\n<p>All this journey has been fun and we thought it will be a good idea to share this with you...</p>\n<p>We hope you enjoy it as much as we have.</p>', 1, 14, 0, 1, 0, 130, 1336646431, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Home', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2549, 'document', 'text/html', 'Wedding Website Improvements and Features', 'Wedding Website Improvements and Features', 'Wedding Website Improvements and Features', 'wedding-website-improvements-and-features', 'Wedding Website Improvements and Features', 1, 0, 0, 6, 0, '', '<p class="bigger">Hello and welcome to The Wedding Website Groups first blog post. Our official launch date which will be in late January 2013 will bring with it a few improvements to the wedding website admin area and the addition of some new wedding website themes. We welcome your feedback for improvements so please do feel free to send your suggestions to<a title="contact the wedding website group" href="mailto:info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com">info@theweddingwebsitegroup.com</a>.</p>\r\n<p>To simplify things here''s a list of improvements we''ll be making over the next few weeks...</p>\r\n<ol class="list-items">\r\n<li><strong>Better facility for sending invitations</strong>- Sending invitations will be improved by allowing you to see exactly what your chosen invitation theme looks like with your event details and guest names.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Additional wedding website themes</strong>- We have been creating our newer wedding website themes so they re-size to fit all mobile devices including the iPhone and iPad. All themes added to the<a title="wedding website themes" href="[[~5]]">designs</a>page from now will be mobile friendly.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Improved text editing</strong>- The area where you add content to your website will be improved to allow you to see more easily how the text will look like once on the actual website.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Font options</strong>- The ability to change font size and font type in the wedding admin area will be added.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2>Thanks to our testers</h2>\r\n<p>Last but by no means least we''d like to thank all the people who have been testing our website and who have prompted the above improvements to be carried out. Without your feedback we wouldn''t have the great product we have now....<em>so thanks!</em></p>', 1, 3, 2, 0, 0, 1, 1356787455, 1, 1356965347, 0, 0, 0, 1356787500, 1, 'Wedding Website Improvements and Features', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(1663, 'document', 'text/html', 'Test newsletter 1', '', '', 'test-newsletter-1', '', 1, 0, 0, 1658, 0, '', '<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/strict.dtd">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<title></title>\r\n<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">\r\n<style type="text/css">\r\na:link, a:visited {\r\n	color: #ee942a;\r\n	text-decoration: underline;\r\n}\r\na:hover {\r\n	color: #a0105c;\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n<meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow"></meta>\r\n<meta property="og:title" content="Experience Zouk"></meta>\r\n</head>\r\n<body bgcolor="#000000" leftmargin="0" topmargin="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0">\r\n<table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n  <tr>\r\n     <tr>\r\n                <td style="height:20px;" >&nbsp;</td>\r\n              </tr>\r\n    <td valign="top" bgcolor="#000000">\r\n    <table width="625" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n    <tr>\r\n	   <td width="312" valign="top" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0">\r\n		<img src="images/img-logo.gif" width="625" height="100">\r\n		</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td valign="top">\r\n        <table width="625" height="400" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n     	\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td colspan="2"  bgcolor="#282828" style="height:1px;" ></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top"><img src="images/img-curry.jpg" width="625" height="395"/></td>\r\n          </tr>\r\n          \r\n        </table></td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      \r\n      <tr>\r\n      	<td bgcolor="#000000" height="5" width="100%"></td>\r\n      </tr>\r\n      <tr>\r\n        <td valign="top" bgcolor="#000000"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">\r\n          <tr>\r\n            <td valign="top">\r\n            <table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n           \r\n              <tr>\r\n  