(2385, 'document', 'text/html', 'Getting here', 'general', 'Custom page', 'custom-page', 'Custom page', 1, 0, 0, 2372, 0, '', '<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">For those of you unfamiliar with this part of the world your journey to the Estate will take you along one of the most beautiful roads in Scotland. </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">Highlights such as Loch Lomond and Glencoe will greet you along the way. It is a fairly straight road but it does include a sailing on the Corran Ferry (ok so at five minutes its a VERY short sailing) after which you head out onto the Morvern peninsular towards the Sound Of Mull.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:Georgia, serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">On leaving the ferry, turn left onto the A861 &amp; continue for approximately 12 miles before turning left for Lochaline &amp; Mull. Follow the stunning (and bendy!) A884keeping an eye open for sheep &amp; deerfor 20 miles until you see a sign for Ardtornish Estate. </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">From there, follow the signs for the wedding. If you reach the village of Lochaline &amp; the seayou have gone too far!!! </span></span></p>\n<p style="line-height:17.8pt;"><span style="font-family:Georgia, serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><img src="../../assets/users/paulandmary/images/map-to-get-to-lochaline-ba5d6712.png" alt="" /></span></span></p>', 1, 33, 12, 1, 0, 1, 1346244857, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Custom page', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
