(2378, 'document', 'text/html', 'Ceremony & Reception', 'general', 'Wedding Party', 'wedding-party', 'Wedding Party', 1, 0, 0, 2372, 0, '', '<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">At the heart of Ardtornish Estate lies a a beautiful Victorian house with a fabulous baronial Hall spilling out onto a huge front lawn with views down Loch Aline to the Isle of Mull. The house and the gardens are expansive (maps will be provide!) therefore, once we''ve arrived there is really no reason for us to leave!! </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><img src="../../assets/users/paulandmary/images/ardtornish-from-the-air-aa19b43b.jpg" alt="" /></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">The ceremony, drinks reception, dinner and dancing will all be held at the House.<span> </span>Timetable for the day will be as follows: </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">2pm Ceremony on the lawn</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">2.30 pm  Drinks reception on the South Wing balcony</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">4.15pm Dinner in the Main Hall</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">7pm Coffee in the Garden flat lounge</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">8pm Let the party begin back in the Main Hall</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">10pm Evening nibbles in the Garden Flat Lounge</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">BedtimeT</span></span><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">here will</span></span><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">be a free bar </span></span><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">provided therefore, no licensing restrictions&amp; no curfew!! </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">Dinner: </span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;">We hadlots of fun coming up with the menu for the wedding and we hope you enjoy the food as much as we enjoyed devising our Flavours of the world menu! Thats all we are going to reveal at this stage however, for those foodies amongst you we can say that the catering is being provided by the Whitehouse Restaurant who are Michelin-listed, lauded in the Rough Guide, Scotland the Best, and.... is one of Hugh Fearnley-Whittingstalls favourite restaurants! </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-size:medium;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">They are absolutely committed to sourcing and serving local, seasonal and organic food. Everything is produced inhouse using Ardtornish beef, venison&amp; lamb, pork from Morvern Fine Pigs, and cheese, crab&amp; mussels from the Isle of Mull. </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">We hope you enjoy it! </span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">Photographs:</span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">We really want to enjoy our day with all of you. We dont want to miss out on the fun &amp; frolics of the drinks reception therefore,we hope to keeptime spentgetting formal photosto an<span> </span>minimum.</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">Rather than an album full of staged photos we''d really like lots &amp; lots of informal shots<span> </span>not only of us, but of all of you too.<span> </span>As such, the photographer will be mingling</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;"></span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:''Poor Richard'', serif;color:#000000;"><span style="font-size:medium;">We only have the photographer for the day of the wedding. So, we have a big ask ofthose of you who are good behind the lens (and those of you who arent) ........pleasebring your cameras,<span> </span>iPhones etc on the Friday to capture the day &amp; evening..if afterwards these photos were to find their way on to the Gallery page of this site well, that would be very much appreciated!</span></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNoSpacing" style="line-height:17.8pt;margin:0cm 0cm 0pt;"><span style="font-family:Georgia, serif;color:#000000;"><span><span style="font-size:medium;"></span></span></span></p>', 1, 33, 5, 1, 0, 1, 1346244857, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Wedding Party', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
