(2169, 'document', 'text/html', 'Reception', 'general', 'Reception', 'reception', 'Reception', 0, 0, 0, 2165, 0, '', '<h1>Reception</h1>\r\n<p>Below are details of our reception...hope you can all make it:</p>\r\n<p>The Big House<br />Valley Parade<br />BD13 2WF</p>\r\n<p><strong>Saturday 21st July</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Start: </strong>7pm<br /><strong>End: </strong>2am</p>\r\n<p>There sill be a buffet with hot and cold sweet and savoury delights. The bar will be open until 2am.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 37, 3, 1, 0, 1, 1341568194, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Reception', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
(2170, 'document', 'text/html', 'Wedding Schedule', 'general', 'Wedding Schedule', 'wedding-schedule', 'Wedding Schedule', 0, 0, 0, 2165, 0, '', '<h1>The Wedding Schedule</h1>\r\n<p>Our Wedding Day details are as follows:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4>2pm - Arrivals at the ceremony</h4>\r\n<p>Ushers 45 minutes before; best man and groom 45-30 minutes\r\nbefore; guests: up to 30 minutes before; groom''s parents: 15\r\nminutes before; mother of bride and bridesmaids ten minutes before;\r\nbride and father five minutes before.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style="font-size: 1em;">The ceremony</h4>\r\n<p>Should last around 30 minutes.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style="font-size: 1em;">Photographs</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n<p>20-30 minutes<br /><em>Note: Allow approximately ten minutes for pictures of the\r\nbride and groom, ten to twenty minutes for other shots.</em></p>\r\n<p><em>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4 style="font-style: normal; font-size: 1em;">Drinks Reception</h4>\r\n</em><em><span style="font-style: normal;">\r\n<p style="display: inline !important;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="display: inline !important;"><em><br />Note: A receiving line takes about 40 minutes and well\r\norganised photographs take 20-30 minutes.</em></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</span></em><em>\r\n<p>\r\n<p style="font-style: normal;">90 minutes, usually extends to two hours</p>\r\n<hr style="font-style: normal;" />\r\n</p>\r\n</em></p>\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h4 style="font-size: 1em;">The wedding meal</h4>\r\n<p>2 hours for a three course meal.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<hr />\r\n<h4>8pm - Evening reception</h4>\r\n<p>Dancing, singing and general merriment will continue until the last guest drops.</p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<hr />\r\n</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</p>\r\n<div id="_mcePaste" class="mcePaste" style="position: absolute; left: -10000px; top: 0px; width: 1px; height: 1px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden;">\r\n<p><em>The following is a rough timeline for the big day, from the\r\nceremony to the end of the reception.</em></p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=Arrivals at the Ceremony&amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">Arrivals at the Ceremony</span></h3>\r\n<p>Ushers 45 minutes before; best man and groom 45-30 minutes\r\nbefore; guests: up to 30 minutes before; groom''s parents: 15\r\nminutes before; mother of bride and bridesmaids ten minutes before;\r\nbride and father five minutes before.</p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Ceremonies" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/ceremonies.aspx">See Ceremonies</a></p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Transport" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/on-the-wedding-day/transport.aspx">See\r\nTransport</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=Church or Civil Ceremony&amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">Church or Civil Ceremony</span></h3>\r\n<p>20-60 minutes (civil ceremonies are shorter than religious\r\nones)</p>\r\n<p><em>N.B. Allow plenty of time to get from the ceremony venue to\r\nthe reception, if applicable, especially if the area is prone to\r\nheavy traffic.</em></p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Ceremonies" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/ceremonies.aspx">See Ceremonies</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=Photographs&amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">Photographs</span></h3>\r\n<p>20-30 minutes</p>\r\n<p><em>Note: Allow approximately ten minutes for pictures of the\r\nbride and groom, ten to twenty minutes for other shots.</em></p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Wedding Photography" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/on-the-wedding-day/wedding-photography.aspx">See Photography</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=Drinks Reception&amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">Drinks Reception</span></h3>\r\n<p>90 minutes, usually extends to two hours</p>\r\n<p><em>Note: A receiving line takes about 40 minutes and well\r\norganised photographs take 20-30 minutes.</em></p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Arrival Drinks" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/reception/food-and-drink/drinks/arrival-drinks.aspx">See Reception Drinks</a></p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Hosting" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/reception/hosting.aspx">See\r\nHosting the Reception</a><a class="bullet" title="Information" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/on-the-wedding-day/guests/information.aspx"></a></p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Information" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/on-the-wedding-day/guests/information.aspx">See Guest Information</a></p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=&lt;br/&gt; &amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate"><br />\r\n</span></h3>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=Seating Guests&amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">Seating Guests</span></h3>\r\n<p>Up to 30 minutes.</p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Seating Plan" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/reception/seating-plan.aspx">See Seating Plan</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=The Wedding Meal&amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">The Wedding Meal</span></h3>\r\n<p>Two hours for three courses.</p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Food and Drink" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/reception/food-and-drink.aspx">See Reception Food &amp; Drink</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=Speeches&amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">Speeches</span></h3>\r\n<p>30 minutes, usually extending to 45 minutes (at least ten\r\nminutes per person, assuming there are three speakers).</p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Speeches" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/reception/speeches.aspx">See\r\nThe Speeches</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=Cake Cutting&amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">Cake Cutting</span></h3>\r\n<p>15-20 minutes.</p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Wedding Cake" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/reception/food-and-drink/wedding-cake.aspx">See Wedding Cake</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 class="sIFR-replaced">\r\n<object style="width: 430px; height: 16px;" width="430" height="16" data="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" type="application/x-shockwave-flash">\r\n<param name="bgcolor" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="flashvars" value="txt=Dancing&amp;textcolor=#0D6CAB&amp;w=430&amp;h=16" />\r\n<param name="src" value="http://www.debretts.com/swf/georgia.swf" />\r\n<param name="wmode" value="transparent" />\r\n<param name="quality" value="best" />\r\n</object>\r\n<span class="sIFR-alternate">Dancing</span></h3>\r\n<p>Approximately three hours.</p>\r\n<p><em>Note: This depends upon when the bride and groom leave, and\r\nhow long the party lasts, and the style of the\r\nvenue/reception.</em></p>\r\n<p><a class="bullet" title="Music" href="http://www.debretts.com/weddings/reception/entertainment/music.aspx">See\r\nEntertainment</a></p>\r\n</div>', 1, 37, 4, 1, 0, 1, 1341568194, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Wedding Schedule', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'modDocument', 'wedding', 1),
