(83, 'registrationUserMail', 'Mail message to the user on registration', 0, 20, 0, 'Thank you for registering with The Wedding Website Group.\n\nWe are pleased to tell you you are amongst the first 50 registrations so your account will automatically be upgraded to the Bronze package meaning you have a FREE one year account.\n\n\nFeedback and Support\n\nThe Wedding Website Group is still in Beta stage which means we are still improving functionality to make it as user friendly as possible. To do this we need your help so we want to encourage you to send us your feedback. You can email us directly at [[+adminemail]] and you can also sign up to the forum which you can find at www.webpods.co.uk/discussion.\nRegistration to the forum only requires an email address, username and a password so it''s simple to sign up.\n\n\nStart Creating Your Website\n\nYour user details are as follows :-\n\nUser Name : [[+username]]\nPassword  : [[+password]]\n\nPlease click the link below to the site to complete your registration and plan your wedding.\n\n[[+registrationValidateLink]]\n\nPlease address any queries or questions you may have about this site to [[+adminemail]].\n\n\n\nThank You.\n\nThe Wedding Website Group\n(trading style of Webpods.co.uk)', 0, 'a:0:{}'),
