(8, 5, 19, '<div class="home-box">\r\n<h3>Save time and money</h3>\r\n<p><img class="alignleft" src="assets/templates/wedding/images/icon-clock.gif" alt="#" />Email invitations and keep guests updated via a blog means you spend less time &amp; money on posting and phoning</p>\r\n<a class="button" title="wedding website features" href="[[~3]]"><span>More features</span></a>\r\n                     </div>\r\n<div class="home-box home-box-padding">\r\n<h3>Makes a great gift</h3>\r\n<p><img class="alignleft" src="assets/templates/wedding/images/icon-giftbag.gif" alt="#" />Why not buy a wedding website package as a gift? We issue vouchers electronically so you can forward to the lucky couple</p>\r\n<a class="button" href="[[~4]]"><span>Buy Now</span></a>\r\n                     </div>\r\n<div class="home-box">\r\n<h3>Unlimited updates</h3>\r\n<p><img class="alignleft" src="assets/templates/wedding/images/icon-laptop.gif" alt="#" />No need to leave your guests guessing, you can update your site as often as you like and alert your guests of any changes...</p>\r\n<a class="button" title="wedding website features" href="[[~3]]"><span>More features</span></a>\r\n                     </div>\r\n<div class="home-box home-box-padding">\r\n<h3>Buy a keepsake DVD</h3>\r\n<p><img class="alignleft" src="assets/templates/wedding/images/icon-dvd.gif" alt="#" />Your wedding/civil partnership website can be a lasting keepsake on a DVD. The DVD will contain all the pages of your final site...</p>\r\n<a class="button" href="[[~3]]"><span>Find out more</span></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<!--.wrapper-->'),
